            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nIn this text, we continue the study begun in the previous work (<htcite0>), on how Indigenous peoples may have carried out mathematical operations in Mesoamerica (Figure 1). Before proceeding, we recommend reading **Chapter 4** of the *First Steps* section (<htcite1>).",
