            {
               "text": "#### Confirming the Result\n\nThe results of the addition and multiplication in Calculation 6 are correct. Now, to confirm the value **882** obtained in Calculation 3, let us make the numerical orders explicit and perform the sums:",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p style=\"text-align=center\"><p><math display=\"block\">  <mn>882</mn> <mo>= (</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>×</mo> <mn>400</mn><mo>) + </mo> <mo>(</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mo>×</mo> <mn>20</mn> <mo>) + </mo> <mo>(</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>×</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>)</mo></math></p> <p><math display=\"block\">  <mn>882</mn> <mo>= (</mo> <mn>800</mn><mo>) + </mo> <mo>(</mo> <mn>80</mn> <mo>) + </mo> <mo>(</mo> <mn>2</mn> <mo>)</mo></math></p>  <p><math display=\"block\">  <mn>882</mn> <mo>= (</mo> <mn>800</mn><mo>) + </mo> <mo>(</mo> <mn>82</mn> <mo>)</mo></math></p> <p><math display=\"block\">  <mn>882</mn> <mo>= </mo> <mn>882</mn></math></p>  <p class=\"desc\">Calculation 7: Rewriting the number 882, making the numerical orders explicit in vigesimal base.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 3: On Calculation 7</b><br /><br />Calculation 7 confirmed the result of Calculation 3. Therefore, we conclude that there is no problem, correct?</div></div></center>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "If, for some reason, the number of verifications seemed excessive, there is no need for concern. This process is part of learning, and throughout life we will always be challenged in our understanding.\n\nIt is important to remember that here we used the vigesimal system, although there is no evidence that this system was used in exactly this way by the Mesoamericans (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>). The Maya numerical system was the calendrical one, already explored in the previous text (<htcite3>).",
